Note: This recipe is vegan and also gluten-free, but only if the soy sauce is non-wheat.\
\
2 shallots\
1 yellow onion\
1 head garlic\
4 hot yellow chilies sliced\
2 tsp ground coriander\
4 tsp ground cumin\
1.5 tsp ground turmeric\
1 tsp ground white pepper\
4 bay leaves\
1 cup strong-tasting vegetable stock\
2 cans chickpeas\
2 carrots sliced\
1 stick celery cut very thinly perpendicular to length\
3/4 cup snow peas\
2 14 oz can coconut milk (1 full-, 1 reduced-fat)\
2 containers firm tofu\
3 Tbsp soy sauce\
3 limes\
4 Tbsp brown sugar\
4 Tbsp tomato puree (or tomato paste + water)\
1 Tsp whole cumin seed\
1/2 cup fresh thai basil\
5 Tbsp coconut oil\
1 cup rice for serving\
